item.title: CVE-2021-21433|2024-08-03T18:16:22.283Z -- demon1a -- discord-recon
item.description: Discord Recon Server is a bot that allows you to do your reconnaissance process from your Discord. Remote code execution in version 0.0.1 would allow remote users to execute commands on the server resulting in serious issues. This flaw is patched in 0.0.2.
